trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) elements in a project.
The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the new <see langword="Target" /> element.
Adds a new [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element to the end of the project.
A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object representing the created <c>Target</c> element.
The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>배열</c>에서 복사를 시작할 인덱스입니다. 이 인덱스는 0부터 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 전체 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />을 호환되는 1차원 <see cref="T:System.Array" />에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
An integer value representing the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> 개체 수를 나타내는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
trans-unit.target: 각 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> 컬렉션의에서 개체를 프로젝트의 요소를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the Target element to search for.
Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> exists in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
<see langword="true" /> if the <c>Target</c> element exists; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <c>Target</c> 요소가 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 사용 하면 호출자가 사용할 수는 `foreach` C# 언어의 (`for each` 에 [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)])는 개인을 반복 하 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> 개체에 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />에 대한 액세스가 동기화되어 스레드로부터 안전하게 보호되는지를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" />에 대한 액세스가 동기화되어 스레드로부터 안전하게 보호되면 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the Target element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 있는 Target 요소의 <see langword="Name" /> 특성입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object that contains the <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target.Name" /> property value specified by <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />로 지정된 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> 속성 값이 포함된 <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target.Name" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object represents a `Target` element in the project.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> 개체가 나타내는 `Target` 는 프로젝트의 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the <see langword="Target" /> element to remove.
Removes the specified [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element from the project.
Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />에 대한 액세스를 동기화하는 데 사용할 수 있는 개체를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />에 대한 액세스를 동기화하는 데 사용할 수 있는 개체입니다.
